title: (Anime-Kraze) Vampire Knight anime Season 1 complete
description:
This is the high quality, English soft-subbed version of Vampire Knight, subbed by Anime-Kraze.org. Video is excellent quality 1280x720, AAC audio, and subtitles in English that can be turned off if you wish. And it all conveniently fits on one DVD-R!

These files are in the MKV container format, you will need a player such as VLC or the Matroska Codec pack to play. There are several good players that can be downloaded for free.

Contains all 13 episodes of the first season. Enjoy and please seed!
